OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782402489
OL,3,CMan has life-threatening injuries
OL,4,Cafter stabbing near football ground
OL,6,FA man is in hospital with life-
OL,7,Fthreatening injuries after a stabbing
OL,8,Fin Cleethorpes.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FBlundell Park at around 8.45am on
OL,12,FThursday 25 June after receiving a
OL,13,Freport of a fight between two men,
OL,14,Fduring which one man was stabbed.
OL,16,FA 26-year-old man is in hospital with
OL,17,Flife-threatening injuries. Another 39-
OL,18,Fyear-old old was taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwith injuries described as serious.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
