PN,33102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782402489
OL,3,CMan has life-threatening injuries
OL,4,Cafter stabbing near football ground
OL,6,FRoads were closed around the incident
OL,7,Fincluding part of Grimsby Road and
OL,8,Ffrom Blundell Avenue in Grimsby to
OL,9,FNevill Street in Cleethorpes.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Tom Kelly of
OL,12,FHumberside Police said that the force
OL,13,Fbelieves the people involved in the
OL,14,Ffight were known to each other and
OL,15,Fthere is no wider risk to the public.
OL,17,FHe said: "Enquiries remain ongoing,
OL,18,Fincluding house to house enquiries,
OL,19,Fand trawling CCTV to establish the
OL,20,Ffull circumstances."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
