FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782402489
OL,3,CMan has life-threatening injuries
OL,4,Cafter stabbing near football ground
OL,6,FThere is expected to be an increased
OL,7,Fpolice presence in the town following
OL,8,Fthe incident.
OL,10,FAsking for people with relevant
OL,11,Fdashcam footage and CCTV from the area
OL,12,Fto come forward, Detective Inspector
OL,13,FKelly said: "I would encourage anyone
OL,14,Fwith information, or anyone with
OL,15,Fconcerns, to please come and speak to
OL,16,Fus."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
